Assignment name  : even_digits
Expected files   : even_digits.c
Allowed functions: write
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Write a program that displays all even digits from 0 to 10 separated by tabs.

The expected output is:

0	2	4	6	8	10

The result must not end with a tab and must be followed by a newline.

Example:

$> ./even_digits
0	2	4	6	8	10$
